word_group.brief_definition: 记日记；写日记；一直记日记

bilingual.source: I won't write in my diary every day.
What about keeping a diary in English?
My learning diary has not been written.
bilingual.target: 我的学习日记还没有写。

bilingual.source: Make a group diary for next weekend.
bilingual.target: 为下个周末做一个小组日记。

bilingual.source: Talk about your group diary to the whole class.
bilingual.target: 向全班谈谈你们的小组日记。

bilingual.source: The original meaning of a journal is a diary about a journey.
bilingual.target: 日记的原意是关于旅行的日记。

list.abstract: DIARY，英文单词，名词，作名词时意为“日志，日记；日记簿”。
《Diary》是由滨崎步伴舞Timothy Wellard作曲，滨崎步作词，miccie演唱的歌曲。收录在miccie的专辑《1st Diary》中。

yingyinNormal.en: No. No. Not my diary. You cannot read my diary.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不要拿我的日记，你不能看我的日记。

yingyinNormal.en: Still, the power of the diary began to scare her. She tried to dispose of it in the girls' bathroom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 日记的力量把她给吓坏了，于是她试着把日记丢到女厕所。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Are you a ghost? A memory, preserved in a diary for 50 years.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是鬼吗？记忆。我是留存在日记中五十年的记忆。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: Dear diary: I'm so excited. My resolution is to write in you every day. I'll see you tomorrow. Nothing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 亲爱的日记：我好兴奋，我的新年新希望是每天写你，我们明天见。什么都没写。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, it's journals and research papers I wrote as a child. Aw, how cute. Is this like a diary? No, that's my potty training journal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是我小时候写的日志与研究报告啦。真有爱这就跟日记一样吗？不是，那是我的如厕训练日志。

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, she gave it to me in a little envelope with her diary key and a list of things she's most afraid of. Maybe we could guess it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是的，她放在一个小信封里，跟她的日记本钥匙以及最怕的事物清单一起交给了我。也许我们能猜出来。

yingyinNormal.en: I knew it wouldn't be safe to open the Chamber again while I was still at school, so I decided to leave behind a diary, preserving my 16-year-old self in its pages so that one day, I would be able to lead another to finish Salazar Slytherin's noble work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在我还待在学校的时候再打开密室实在是太冒险了，所以我决定留下我的日记，把十六岁的我保存在日记里头，直到有一天我能够引导另一个人来完成萨拉札斯莱特林的伟大使命。
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets》

yingyinNormal.en: And what about you? Well, I don't keep my diary in my head. Ask me nearer the time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你呢？我哪能记住日程，时间再近些再问我吧。

yingyinNormal.en: I just had a look through my diary for the next two months and my next day off is in about a month and a half, just over that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我看了我接下来两个月的日程，我下次休假是在一个半月后，甚至更往后。
yingyinNormal.videoNameZh: 《大卫·贝克汉姆：探索未知之境》

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: But as adults we also have the luxury of being able to control our own <highlight>diaries</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是作为成年人，我们有能力掌管自己的日记。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

word_usage.usage:
diary表“日记”, “日记簿”时，为可数名词，其复数形式是diaries。“写日记”用keep a diary表达。
示例：我每天都写日记。
误 I note diary every day.
正 I keep a diary every day.
正 I write a diary every day.
